{"serial": "34041", "department_serial": 30, "code": "CH8120", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Applied Microbial Engineering", "ch": "微生物應用工程"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "研究所領域分類：化工類"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Shu, Chin-Hang"], "ch": ["徐敬衡"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["2", "3", "4"]}, "loc": {"building": "E", "room": "233"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 65, "department": {"ch": "化學工程與材料工程學系", "en": "Department of  Chemical Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "碩博同修", "en": "Master/Doctoral Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 32, "remark": {"ch": "研究所領域分類：化工類", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "微生物簡單的來說，係指我們在日常生活中隨處可遇著的細菌、病毒及真菌。如各舉一個簡單的例子來看，大腸桿菌是大家所相當熟悉的細菌種類；B型肝炎的致病原 因B型肝炎病毒就是一種病毒；而相當美味可口的食用菇類，就是真菌的一種(分成酵母菌、黴菌與蕈類)。微生物在「生物科技」產業上可說是用處多多，以 下將分別就其在醫藥、農業、環保，及食品等各方面的應用。", "en": "This course provides insights into multiple applications using microbes to promote productivity in agriculture, to produce biochemicals or to respond to challenges in biomedicine. It highlights the microbial production of nanocompounds with medical functionality alongside new anti-mycobacterial strategies, and introduces plant-growth-promoting Rhizobacteria as well as the correlation between biofilm formation and crop productivity."}, "outline": {"ch": "課程介紹\nCh. 1 微生物醫藥工業：疫苗(如B型肝炎疫苗)\nCh. 2 微生物醫藥工業：抗生素\nCh. 3 微生物醫藥工業：干擾素\nCh. 4 微生物食品工業：傳統釀造技術(如酒、醋、醬油等)\nCh. 5 微生物食品工業)：抗菌物質(如由乳酸菌所產生的nisin等)\nCh. 6 微生物食品工業：保健菌株\nCh. 7 微生物農業工業：生長促進劑\nCh. 8 微生物農業工業：害蟲防治劑\nCh. 9 微生物農業工業：誘發作物抗性之製劑\nCh. 10 微生物環保工業：「生物復育」(Bioremediation)\nCh. 11 微生物環保工業：分解油污\nCh. 12 微生物環保工業：分解有機廢棄物\n研究專題口頭報告", "en": "Introduction\nCh. 1 Medical Application:vaccine\nCh. 2 Medical Application: antibiotics\nCh. 3 Medical Application: Interferon\nCh. 4 Food Industry：traditional fermentation products\nCh. 5 Food Industry：nisins\nCh. 6 Food Industry：health care\nCh. 7 Agricultural Application：plant growth stimulants\nCh. 8 Agricultural Application：insecticides\nCh. 9 Agricultural Application：tolerant to stress\nCh. 10 Environmental Application：Bioremediation\nCh. 11 Environmental Application：oil removal\nCh. 12 Environmental Application：organic waste recycle\nReports"}, "textbook": {"ch": "A Textbook of Biotechnology\n作者：RC Dubey\n出版者 ‏ : ‎ S. Chand Publishing (2022年 1月 1日)\n語言 ‏ : ‎ English\nISBN-10 ‏ : ‎ 9355010532\nISBN-13 ‏ : ‎ 978-9355010537", "en": "A Textbook of Biotechnology\n作者：RC Dubey\n出版者 ‏ : ‎ S. Chand Publishing (2022年 1月 1日)\n語言 ‏ : ‎ English\nISBN-10 ‏ : ‎ 9355010532\nISBN-13 ‏ : ‎ 978-9355010537"}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "40%", "en": "40%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n\n\n個別指導", "en": ["Lecture", "", "", "Individual Instruction"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "(1) 口頭報告 (占評分 40％)、\n(2) 書面報告 (占評分40％)、       \n(3) 出席 (占評分20％)", "en": "(1) Oral Report口 (40％)、\n(2) Written Report (40％)、       \n(3) attendance (20％)"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週四 中午12:00~14:00", "en": "Thursday 12:00~14:00"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "18", "en": "18"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "domain": {"ch": "化材工程專業課程\n\n\n、\n\n\n尖端生化工程", "en": "化材工程專業課程\n\n\n、\n\n\n尖端生化工程"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "專業領域知識", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "學術研究", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評"]}, {"competencies": "專業論文撰寫", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "無"]}, {"competencies": "創新思考", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "協調整合", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "國際視野", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["作業練習", "口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "領導管理", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["口頭報告/口試", "專題研究報告(書面)", "實作/實驗", "出席/課堂表現", "學習檔案評量", "自我評量/同儕互評", "作品/創作展演"]}, {"competencies": "終身學習", "rating": "(4)高", "ass